author: Zeta Ret, Ivo Yankulovski
text: Interface Generator, Mass Class/Header Resolve, Function Decomposer, Class Parser, ProtoSS-XeltoSS Transformator

public_methods.unpackCaliber: clbrname*: String, toppack: Object, xeltoss: Boolean; return Array
public_methods.caliberClass: name*: String, supers*: Array, settings*: Object, defname: Boolean, superargs: null|Boolean|Object, supertype: Boolean; return Function

descriptions.useXeltoSS: Use XeltoSS Configuration to transform ProtoSS Function Class to XeltoSS ES6 Class
descriptions.calibers: Package of settings, includes Array of Caliber ProtoSS Function

Clockwork.this: constructor, creates Clockwork object based on ProtoSS and XeltoSS

unpackCaliber.this: Creates Array of Caliber ProtoSS Function from package of settings
unpackCaliber.return: array of functions, headers are auto resolved

xeltossCaliber.this: Transforms the entire Caliber Package into XeltoSS ES6 Classes

caliberClass.this: Creates ProtoSS Function from Settings Object, includes shared memory, serial number, original settings, and adjacent methods
caliberClass.name: name of the caliber class
caliberClass.supers: array of ProtoSS Function Classes to inherit
caliberClass.settings: calibration settings object embedded in the final class
caliberClass.superargs: arguments passed to inherited classes in super call
caliberClass.supertype: switch between superList and superList2 prototype

runXeltoSS.this: Transforms an Array of ProtoSS Function into XeltoSS ES6 Classes, reading __xeltoss_amaps, __xeltoss_emaps, __xeltoss_eamaps, __xeltoss_augmentmap, __xeltoss_embedmap, __xeltoss_prepare, supports debug state
runXeltoSS.xcls: executes augmentKey/addEmbedMap using __xeltoss_amaps:Array and __xeltoss_emaps:Array, __xeltoss_eamaps:Array is mapped version of augmentKey/addEmbedMap, __xeltoss_augmentmap:Object is custom augmentKey, __xeltoss_embedmap:Object is custom addEmbedMap, __xeltoss_prepare is custom function using ProtoSS function scope
